# ðŸ”· Data Flow â€” Case Upload to Discovery

### Case Creation Flow

1. Family uploads photos + details
2. API Gateway validates + rate limits
3. Case Service stores metadata
4. Images â†’ Object Storage
5. AI Service triggered by Kafka event
6. Face embeddings â†’ Vector DB
7. OSINT crawler activated
8. Search index updated
9. Police verification requested
10. Public listing published

---

### Tip Processing Flow

1. Citizen submits tip
2. Tip Service stores submission
3. AI analyses media
4. Geo-clustering applied
5. Priority score calculated
6. Police dashboard updated
7. Alerts triggered if threshold crossed

