# ðŸ”· Security Architecture

## Identity & Access

* OAuth2 + device fingerprinting
* Police smart-card login
* NGO role tokens
* RBAC + ABAC combined
* Session-level audit logging

---

## Data Protection

* AES-256 at rest
* TLS 1.3 in transit
* Separate biometric vault
* Key rotation via HSM
* Tokenization for public views

---

## Abuse Controls

* CAPTCHA + rate limits
* Duplicate case detection
* Sybil resistance
* Shadow banning
* Court-order unlock mechanism

